Class BasicTabDisplayerUI.BasicModelListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.netbeans.swing.tabcontrol.plaf.AbstractTabDisplayerUI.ModelListener
      • org.netbeans.swing.tabcontrol.plaf.BasicTabDisplayerUI.BasicModelListener
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    EventListener, ChangeListener, ListDataListener, ComplexListDataListener
    Enclosing class:
    BasicTabDisplayerUI

    protected class BasicTabDisplayerUI.BasicModelListener
extends AbstractTabDisplayerUI.ModelListener
    Listener on data model which will pass modified indices to the TabState object, so it can update which tab indices are flashing in "attention" mode, if any.
